            <title>[CXF-3369] jetty SecurityHandler should be on top of org.apache.cxf.transport.http_jetty.JettyHTTPHandler</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-3369</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;we can configure jetty SecurityHandler through httpj:handlers to enable jetty server side security such as basic auth, but SecurityHandler should on top of org.apache.cxf.transport.http_jetty.JettyHTTPHandler.&lt;br/&gt;
Also will add a testcase to demonstrate how to enable jetty server basic auth with configuring the SecurityHandler.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
